high_descs: Turn around and walk to the counter where the knives are.
Pick up the silver-handled knife from the counter.
Turn around and walk to the white dining table.
Place the knife in the silver bowl.
Pick up the silver bowl from the table.
Turn around and walk back to the counter where the knives are.
Put the bowl with the knife on the counter.
Turn left and walk up to the white table, then turn left and walk over to the counter.
Pick up the butter knife off of the counter.
Turn right and walk over to the wall, then turn right again and walk up to the white table.
Put the butter knife in the bowl on the table.
Pick up the bowl with the butter knife in it.
Turn right and begin walking across the room, then turn right and walk over to the counter.
Put the bowl with the butter knife in it onto the right side of the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl with a butter knife in it on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the counter across the room.
Pick up the butter knife on the edge of the counter.
Turn to the right and walk to the edge of the table with the white bowl and blue plate.
Put the knife in the white bowl on the right.
Pick up the white bowl to the right of the blue plate.
Turn around and walk to the counter.
Put the bowl down on the right side of the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a knife in a bowl on the counter.
